 Pod - Attribute Value Menu

 The attribute value menu gives access to two
 "per  value"  operations:   "undo  changes" and 
 "delete value".

 The "undo changes" operation undoes all changes
 since the last succesful submission of modifications,
 or else restores the original attribute value.

 The "delete value" operation deletes the associated
 attribute value.


